  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>When you infuse your weapon with arcane might, your attacks make foes more susceptible to magic.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Arcane Strike, ability to cast arcane spells.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>If you have a weapon that is augmented by your Arcane Strike feat, when you damage a creature with an attack made with that weapon, that creature takes a -2 penalty on saving throws against spells and spell-like abilities. This effect lasts for 1 round.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you use this feat, you can spend up to 3 stamina points to increase the duration of the effect by 1 round for each stamina point spent.",
